abstract:

Speaker:: Theodore Meynard Track: PyData: Data Handling I will introduce the concept of data unit tests and why they are important in the workflow of data scientists when building data products. In this talk, you will learn a new tool you can use to ensure the quality of the products you build. Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2022 conference, April 11-13 2022. https://2022.pycon.de More details at the conference page: https://2022.pycon.de/program/MPWLWP Twitter: https://twitter.com/pydataberlin Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconde
